{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-29-distinct-powers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 29: Različite sile","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Istražite sve vrednosti za $a^b$ za $2 \\le a \\le 5$ i $2 \\le b \\le 5$:</p>\n<div style='padding-left: 4em;'>\n  2<sup>2</sup>=4, 2<sup>3</sup>=8, 2<sup>4</sup>=16, 2<sup>5</sup>=32 <br>\n  3<sup>2</sup>=9, 3<sup>3</sup>=27, 3<sup>4</sup>=81, 3<sup>5</sup>=243 <br>\n  4<sup>2</sup>=16, 4<sup>3</sup>=64, 4<sup>4</sup>=256, 4<sup>5</sup>=1024 <br>\n  5<sup>2</sup>=25, 5<sup>3</sup>=125, 5<sup>4</sup>=625, 5<sup>5</sup>=3125 <br>\n</div>\n<p>Ako se zatim poređaju po numeričkom redosledu i ukloni svako ponavljanje, dobijamo ovu sekvencu od 15 različitih reči:</p>\n<div style='padding-left: 4em;'>\n  4, 8, 9, 16, 25, 27, 32, 64, 81, 125, 243, 256, 625, 1024, 3125\n</div>\n<p>Koliko je različitih elemenata u nizu generisanom sa $a^b$ za 2 ≤ <code>a</code> ≤ <code>n</code> i 2 ≤ <code>b</code> ≤ <code>n</code>?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3891000cf542c50fe9c","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301941,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-29-distinct-powers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function distinctPowers(n) {\n\n  return n;\n}\n\ndistinctPowers(30);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>distinctPowers(15)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof distinctPowers(15) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>distinctPowers(15)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati 177.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(distinctPowers(15), 177);"},{"text":"<p><code>distinctPowers(20)</code> trebalo bi vratiti 324.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(distinctPowers(20), 324);"},{"text":"<p><code>distinctPowers(25)</code> treba da vrati 519.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(distinctPowers(25), 519);"},{"text":"<p><code>distinctPowers(30)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 755.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(distinctPowers(30), 755);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-29-distinct-powers","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-30-digit-n-powers","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-28-number-spiral-diagonals","id":"5900f3891000cf542c50fe9c","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-29-distinct-powers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}